{"tid":2487752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到頭來政府都只係為左要大家打疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-13T20:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:15:10.000Z","uid":222614,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc646497ff444d129beb86d8ad6bd2c8568f2e7","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:26:12.000Z","msg":"都話左你係估唔到政府想點<br />\n<br />\n人地有錢請學者，有錢做 research，有錢買 data，有錢做 analysis，每個決策都用左唔知幾多錢，背後有唔知幾多 science 做 backup<br />\n<br />\n不在體制內嘅香港人如果想早啲知道政府想點，唯有全職去做分析先有機會 ...."},{"pid":"d89a80b99287e3d2bd13806b122bdc90f7d8e400","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:29:45.000Z","msg":"係政府眼中只有兩種人：接受疫苗同拒絕疫苗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n你有無見過體制內嘅人拒絕疫苗而可以留任？即使依家尚餘些少自由，可以畀人決定打唔打，但最後政府一定有方法令人屈服 ...."},{"pid":"3080e69ddb52a95a930f7643c773830f09015ddc","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:34:10.000Z","msg":"自問對得住良心，打復必泰而唔打科興嘅，請問你係政府眼中同打科興嘅有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n政府一樣有你嘅接種紀綠係佢 system 存留，第時會畀個 ID 你隨身携帶<br />\n出入場所有特別嘅待遇，到時你可以謝絕優待，但你已經係佢地嘅一份子了 ...."},{"pid":"fdce411c7ca4d155e06ca6246b6885ff3f7a5040","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:35:58.000Z","msg":"重覆：政府根本唔 care 你打邊隻疫苗，只要你肯打"},{"pid":"d81589c07703ebecf9c8251e16bd749355680077","tid":2487752,"uid":38177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"啱阿，多人打就夠料做健康碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad615fdc644c23604961ec91cb60f7945a3b5384","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:50:50.000Z","msg":"有人上黎放風話不分化，只要唔打科興就係手足<br />\n<br />\n但唔好望記只要打過疫苗，政府 system 都有紀錄<br />\n第時會對你有優待，即使你打曬鑼鼓咁反科興撐復必泰<br />\n<br />\n所以如果大家真係諗住打復必泰可以順便對政府表示否定，表逹自己嘅不滿，同埋對得住良心，咁你己經中左伏<br />\n<br />\n如果你打復必泰單純因為信得過佢，又想有所謂嘅保護就無問題<br />\n但唔好講到㨂某隻唔㨂另一隻就代表自己企係正義嘅一邊<br />\n你咁樣只會令堅持拒絕疫苗嘅香港人係將來變成少數，受越多嘅欺壓"},{"pid":"865f1dbdb47841cef0aef4efcffeb9e6fd69ac47","tid":2487752,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81589c07703ebecf9c8251e16bd749355680077","tid":2487752,"uid":38177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"啱阿，多人打就夠料做健康碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:59:20.000Z","msg":"樓主PIN　THIS啦"},{"pid":"7c2506676a02decd4a67a4ad06a9f35cb4046bb9","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"865f1dbdb47841cef0aef4efcffeb9e6fd69ac47","tid":2487752,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81589c07703ebecf9c8251e16bd749355680077","tid":2487752,"uid":38177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"啱阿，多人打就夠料做健康碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:59:20.000Z","msg":"樓主PIN　THIS啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"sor .... 我覺得依家個句重要啲 ...."},{"pid":"0de51f137f7e61af5ccd2ee13313b74a90911a10","tid":2487752,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c2506676a02decd4a67a4ad06a9f35cb4046bb9","tid":2487752,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"865f1dbdb47841cef0aef4efcffeb9e6fd69ac47","tid":2487752,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81589c07703ebecf9c8251e16bd749355680077","tid":2487752,"uid":38177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"啱阿，多人打就夠料做健康碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:59:20.000Z","msg":"樓主PIN　THIS啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"sor .... 我覺得依家個句重要啲 ...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T21:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aaa3ea34d905996fa9fae0ef512fb8c0b393360","tid":2487752,"ui